    "description": "*这个游戏在SteamDeck上表现优异，稳定的帧率令人满意。<br><br>1、一场关于梦境的奇妙冒险 <br>探索你的伙伴奥莉薇娅的梦境空间，这里非常美丽，但违背现实的常理，同时也遍布了各种障碍与危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330680/extras/19edfa024e93db7c678a531b79af793e.poster.avif?t=1694019244\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330680/extras/19edfa024e93db7c678a531b79af793e.webm?t=1694019244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330680/extras/19edfa024e93db7c678a531b79af793e.mp4?t=1694019244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>2、与时间赛跑 <br>你的每次进入都会遭到奥莉薇娅潜意识的排异而直接中止。因此，你必须在有限的时间内妥善地分配获取力量和挑战Boss的时间。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330680/extras/bb0a0995841f788f199dc591bdb25f7d.poster.avif?t=1694019244\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330680/extras/bb0a0995841f788f199dc591bdb25f7d.webm?t=1694019244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330680/extras/bb0a0995841f788f199dc591bdb25f7d.mp4?t=1694019244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>3、极具挑战性的Boss战斗 <br>奥莉薇娅的每个幻想人格都具有独特的战斗风格和强大的压迫感，你需要克服恐惧并妥善管理你的精力槽。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330680/extras/5308cab004daebd6ee0781fe28f1a8fa.poster.avif?t=1694019244\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330680/extras/5308cab004daebd6ee0781fe28f1a8fa.webm?t=1694019244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330680/extras/5308cab004daebd6ee0781fe28f1a8fa.mp4?t=1694019244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>4、丰富的忍术技能 <br>二十余种忍术技能将会随机出现在关卡中，使每场战斗中的你都成为独一无二的忍者。<br><br>曾经有那么一段时间，我拥有一个幻想出来的朋友。 <br>他一直陪伴着我，直到我不再感到孤独，然后他却消失不见了。 <br>或许，你也曾经有过幻想的朋友。<br><br>因此，我独自开发了这款游戏，希望大家都能记得自己曾经的伙伴和美好。",
